# Waiting Screen Mod

Server-side waiting room system for Minecraft Fabric 1.21.1

## Installation

1. Download from Releases
2. Place in `mods/` folder
3. Add images to `config/waitingscreens/`

## Commands

- `/waitingscreen start <players>` - Start waiting
- `/waitingscreen stop` - Stop waiting
- `/waitingscreen screen <name>` - Change image

